1. Information We Collect
We collect and process the following types of information when you use the Bot:

User Information: The Bot may collect your Discord username, ID, avatar, and server information to interact with you and deliver requested services.
Usage Data: We collect usage statistics, including commands used, interactions with the Bot, and any messages sent to the Bot, to improve the performance and functionality of the Bot.
Bot Commands: The Bot logs all interactions (commands) made by users. This includes data like the command issued, the time, and any specific arguments or parameters provided in the command.
2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To provide the services and features of the Bot.
To monitor and analyze usage to improve the Botâ€™s functionality and user experience.
To send you updates, notifications, and support messages related to the Bot.
3. Data Retention
We will retain your information only for as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy. We retain data for the following durations:

Interaction Logs: Retained for up to 30 days to analyze usage and improve the Bot.
Personal Information: We do not store your personal information beyond what is necessary for interaction with the Bot (e.g., Discord username and ID).
